nhc_headline: ...OCTAVE STRENGTHENS OVER THE OPEN TROPICAL EASTERN PACIFIC...
summary: ...OCTAVE STRENGTHENS OVER THE OPEN TROPICAL EASTERN PACIFIC... As of 2:00 AM MST Wed Oct 01 the center of Octave was located near 11.1, -114.8 with movement NNW at 7 mph. The minimum central pressure was 996 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 60 mph.
